# Controlled Dynamics Inc - Claude Code Project Configuration

This is a Next.js project for Controlled Dynamics Inc., a precision engineering and motion control solutions company.

## Project Information
- **Name:** Controlled Dynamics Inc.
- **Domain:** controlleddynamicsinc.com
- **Framework:** Next.js 16 with App Router
- **Language:** TypeScript
- **Styling:** Tailwind CSS

## Quick Commands
- `npm run dev` - Start development server
- `npm run build` - Build for production
- `npm start` - Start production server
- `./EXECUTE_DEPLOYMENT.sh` - Deploy to Heroku

## URLs
- Development: http://localhost:3000
- Production: https://controlleddynamicsinc.com
- Heroku: https://controlleddynamicsinc-9454610b5597.herokuapp.com
- GitHub: https://github.com/watchdogpedro/controlleddynamicsinc.com
